title: Collect OptProf data on x64 machine.
body:
We currently collect optimization data on the `X86` machines. 
According to measurements available at this moment for other repos, this should affect the optimization data much, but I would rather move collection to `X64` machines and check this for msbuild (see [this ](https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild/pull/8085#pullrequestreview-1156242133)comment).
